rows.label: tlk70000048_05_msg0001
rows.name:
To think that there would have been a
monster attack! Thank you all for
lending us your strength.

rows.label: tlk70000048_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Noowl and the kids let me in on all
the details.

rows.label: tlk70000048_05_msg0003
rows.name:
I had duties elsewhere and wasn't here
at the time. At least it seems like the
enemy didn't have it together...

rows.label: tlk70000048_05_msg0004
rows.name:
After the attack, the other leaders and
I met to come up with a plan from here
on out.

rows.label: tlk70000048_05_msg0005
rows.name:
Even Augusto seemed riled up and
eager to iron out a plan. Not sure I've
ever seen him so worked up.
